{"tid":1930112,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[沒事兒 照搞]日本奧委會副主席田島幸三確診","createTime":"2020-03-17T10:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T11:13:56.000Z","uid":35562,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"215682de43b481ef168c67d001337e05a1d41f99","tid":1930112,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:40:52.000Z","msg":"據日本共同社報道，消息人士周二（17日）透露，日本足協主席、奧委會副主席田島幸三新冠病毒的檢測結果呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，田島除擔任日本足協主席外，還擔任國際足聯理事、東京奧組委副主席等多個體育團體的要職。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，田島在2月和3月這段時間，曾因出席會議、申辦女足世界盃和視察友誼賽等到過英國、荷蘭和美國。"},{"pid":"1384e07e413971c2f31d430564f487aebcc566a3","tid":1930112,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d0561d739964f1691a013640c1fdca42d33226","tid":1930112,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e406f866d62a5726464ee8641c0c9300ca17d29","tid":1930112,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63fa1b2de1ee15c3fca64dd6f20b641632b6c2d","tid":1930112,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b617b5a386ac14ec3bc4f8565b2beeb6ed15a6d3","tid":1930112,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264e773c4f4e5264b31ed1239300a8fb145a2baf","tid":1930112,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"<i